{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friendly Facade is a visual novel with point and click and strategy mini-games incorporated into key story moments to immerse the player in the experience. The game explores how each character's background and strongly held ideals inform their personality, decision-making, and strategy in tense situations. Every character has their own goals and motivations and form a web of interpersonal relationships that intersect and collide with each other to form a rich, nuanced story where not everyone is able to get a happy ending. Inside the peaceful confines of the Isolated Society Study, competition, manipulation, and betrayal run rampant, and this is <i>before</i> the Golding Foundation intervenes, changing the rules of the game, and the fates of those 16 individuals trapped within it, forever...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you solve the mystery of the Golding Foundation, and dispel the facades that all 16 characters in this story use to mask their deepest, darkest secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are currently 7 chapters available to play with more actively in development. Currently, the first chapter has voice acting content with more planned for the future. The word count is ~190,000 and there are ~150 CGs.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732889002","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256920/page.bg.jpg?t=1732889002","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256920/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732889002","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256920/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732889002","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This game contains blood, death, and hea